		<span id="title-175712561" class="story-title"> <a   href="//slashdot.org/story/24/12/20/1816259/why-online-returns-are-a-hassle-now">Why Online Returns Are a Hassle Now</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theatlantic.com/newsletters/archive/2024/12/online-returns-hassle-fees-fraud/681084/"  title="External link - https://www.theatlantic.com/newsletters/archive/2024/12/online-returns-hassle-fees-fraud/681084/" target="_blank"> (theatlantic.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
